quran[8{c,v,t}:
57,4,wohi hai jis ne asmano aur zameen ko chay din mein pedakiya phir arsh par ja thehra. jo cheez zameen mein daakhil hoti aur jo is se nikalti hai aur jo aasman se utartee aur jo is ki taraf chadhti hai sab is ko maloom hai. aur tum jahan kahin ho woh tumahray sath hai. aur jo kuch tum karte ho khuda is ko dekh raha hai
57,5,asmano aur zameen ki badshahi isi ki hai. aur sab umoor isi ki taraf rujoo hotay hain
57,6,raat ko din mein daakhil karta aur din ko raat mein daakhil karta hai. aur woh dilon ke bheidoon taq se waaqif hai
57,7,to ) khuda par aur is ke rasool par imaan lao aur jis ( maal ) mein is ne tum ko ( apna ) naib banaya hai is mein se kharch karo. jo log tum mein se imaan laaye aur ( maal ) kharch karte rahay un ke liye bara sawab hai
57,8,aur tum kaisay log ho ke khuda par imaan nahi laatay. halaank ( is ke ) paighambar tumhe bulaa rahay hain ke apne perwar-digaar par imaan lao aur agar tum ko bawar ho to woh tum se ( is ka ) ehad bhi le chuka hai
57,9,wohi to hai jo apne bande par wazeh ( اul matalib ) ayatain nazil karta hai taakay tum ko andheron mein se nikaal kar roshni mein laaye. be shak khuda tum par nihayat shafqat karne wala ( aur ) meharban hai
57,10,aur tum kokiya howa hai ke khuda ke raste mein kharch nahi karte halaank asmano aur zameen ki waarsat khuda hi ki hai. jis shakhs ne tum mein se fatah ( mecca ) se pehlay kharchkiya aur larai ki woh ( aur jis ne yeh kaam peechay kiye woh ) barabar nahi. un ka darja un logon se kahin barh kar hai jinhon ne baad mein kharch ( amwal ) aur ( kufar se ) jehaad o qitaal kiya. aur khuda ne sab se ( sawab ) naik ( ka ) wada tokiya hai. aur jo kaam tum karte ho khuda un se waaqif hai
57,11,kon hai jo khuda ko ( niyat ) naik ( aur khuloos se ) qarz day to woh is ko is se dugna kere aur is ke liye izzat ka sila ( yani jannat ) hai
